@ExamM2.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5149

### GET Products
GET {{ExamM2.Api_HostAddress}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### POST Order - Simple
POST {{ExamM2.Api_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### POST Order - With quantity > 5 (10% discount on product)
POST {{ExamM2.Api_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "id": 5,
      "quantity": 6
    }
  ]
}

###

### POST Order - With valid promo code
POST {{ExamM2.Api_HostAddress}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "id": 3,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "promo_code": "DISCOUNT20"
}

